column5: Well as complete as its gonna get for now!  We've been spending every spare minute since Mid June up there.. countless loads in.. every favor I could possibly call in used.. lol.. Only twice on the water all summer....BUT were back in business, and get to spend the last week of the summer up at camp for our 25th anniversary.. with the kids before they go off to school.  Im a happy feller, what a relief to be done. Just some tweaking left to finish!  (and a new crapper to boot!)  From This:        To THIS!!
Does Irish know which rock the key is under?
LOL.. It aint locked... and it aint ever gunna be!
Just a padlock on the beer fridge then?
Sucks when mother nature forces yer hand, but the end result of this is pretty nice.  The place looks awesome.
Lookin' good TJ. Needs a little attic insulation before the snow flies. Hopefully my cabin comes together as nicely.
Wow !!!! Awesome looking TJ !!!! When is the ofc get together !!!! Lol ... Great place to be that's for sure ... Quite the progress from a few years ago !!! Cheers
